  "description": "Get your team outside and on the water with Premier Party Cruises' Lake Travis boat rentals. Perfect for corporate team bonding, employee appreciation, and team outings. Private boats for 14-75 guests with licensed, experienced captains and clean facilities. Lake Travis provides the ideal setting for team events - away from office distractions in a relaxed outdoor environment where teams naturally connect. The shared experience of being on the water, swimming (when conditions are safe), and enjoying Austin's natural beauty creates lasting bonds. Everything is delivered and set up for you - easy for office administrators, unforgettable for your team. Choose from Standard (boat, captain, coolers, sound system), Essentials (adds ice, water dispenser, cups, table), or Ultimate (adds floats, disco ball cups, bubbles, sunscreen, plates) packages. BYOB friendly (cans/plastic only, 21+). We can help coordinate alcohol delivery through Party On Delivery. Fleet accommodates 14-75 guests across boats. Additional crew fees: $50/hour for 26-30 guests, $100/hour for 51-75 guests.",
